            <h1 class="slideHeader">Developer, Entrepreneur, Beard Enthusiast</h1>
            <br>
            <br>
            <p>
                I am an I.T. Professional located in Louisville, Kentucky. Currently employed at ZirMed, I am an I.T. Intern within their Architecture
